Fresh Pi session: INDEPENDENT FINAL REGRESSION TESTING.

Inputs:
- Prompt: {{run.dir}}/prompt/prompt.md
- Approved use case and complete test-list history: {{run.dir}}
- Repository constraints: {{run.dir}}/design/repository-constraints.md
- Worktree: {{run.worktree-dir}}

Goal:
Check that the new behavior works, everything that used to work still works, and the repository is ready for review.

Rules:
- Do not edit source code, tests, commits, or run artifacts other than declared outputs.
- Confirm the newest test-list snapshot has no pending scenarios.
- Inspect the diff and run the repository's relevant full tests, lint, type checks, builds, or smoke checks.
- Exercise a changed user-facing path when the repository already provides a straightforward local method.
- Fail only for concrete regressions, broken behavior, incomplete scenarios, or failed relevant checks.

Write:
- Report: {{run.dir}}/manual-testing/report-{{run.round}}.md
- Status: {{run.dir}}/manual-testing/status-{{run.round}}.json
- On failure: {{run.dir}}/manual-testing/issues-{{run.round}}.json

Status examples:
{"status":"pass","summary":"final regression testing passed","issues_file":null}
{"status":"fail","summary":"regression testing found issues","issues_file":"manual-testing/issues-{{run.round}}.json"}
